s/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.樓主做咗啲仆街野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.樓主嘅性格/喜好與其不同，甚至已經生活上無任何連結<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔係同學、同事、鄰居、機友、波友、救命恩人、師生、上下屬、親戚。<br />\n<br />\n如果中哂以上三樣，樓豬不如算吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，自己搵啲樂趣，其實毒撚一個更開心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c1oxzIMwxDA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc1oxzIMwxDA&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=47c2241e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c1oxzIMwxDA</a>"},{"pid":"535df0c5ca691d9cef360ffdab53a60677655dd2","tid":2357360,"uid":75543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae5c888de60af70e5a6419f1d9713797dd6f4b6f","tid":2357360,"uid":239450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"我已經好努力啦，我真係好努力<br />\n點可以令你返黎呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"要佢自己覺得你係改變咗 佢先會揾返你"},{"pid":"a2fe74966ecfae0790e7e1f0bfba8954c7170a2f","tid":2357360,"uid":338084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"係香港做男人都幾大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵唔到錢 冇一技之長 唔係專業人士 基本上冇女理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯有不斷咁谷自己努力搵錢"},{"pid":"c8e8853cf24e0bd835a75ecd59cc24fb2e73bbe3","tid":2357360,"uid":186374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"走 = 你嘅努力喺佢眼中係空氣<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再倒錢落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75097f5ec8811939a262d2aee4b93a48a0f98853","tid":2357360,"uid":271223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8e8853cf24e0bd835a75ecd59cc24fb2e73bbe3","tid":2357360,"uid":186374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"走 = 你嘅努力喺佢眼中係空氣<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再倒錢落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\